title: TIP4 - Phase II LON Liquidity Incentive (LON 二期流动性激励)
body:
Background
* According to the Tokenlon litepaper, 10,000,000 LON is reserved for liquidity related incentives.
* The core team kicked off Phase I LON Liquidity Incentive on December 24, 2020 with 1,500,000 LON reward in total. The phase is about to end on January 21, 2021.
* The team plans to start Phase II LON Liquidity Incentive on January 21, 2021. It will last for 6 weeks and end on March 4, 2021. LON will be rewarded in the same way to the below two liquidity pools:
  * LON/ETH pool on Uniswap
  * LON/USDT pool on Sushiswap

Goal
* Let the community decide on the number of LON used for Phase II LON Liquidity Incentive

Proposed Action Items
* Make changes based on the voting results of the proposal, and take effect at 4:00 UTC on January 21, 2021.

Voting Options
* A. Each of the two pools receives 500,000 LON as the Phase II Liquidity Incentive
* B. Each of the two pools receives 600,000 LON as the Phase II Liquidity Incentive
* C. Each of the two pools receives 700,000 LON as the Phase II Liquidity Incentive
* D. Each of the two pools receives 800,000 LON as the Phase II Liquidity Incentive

---

背景
* 根据 Tokenlon litepaper，10,000,000 LON 可被用于流动性相关激励。
* 核心团队已于 2020.12.24 开启第一期流动性激励。该激励于 2021.1.21 结束，共使用 1,500,000 LON。
* 核心团队计划于 2021.1.21 开启第二期流动性激励，为期 6 周，于 2021.3.4 结束。二期将采用同样的形式激励以下两个流动性池：
  * Uniswap 上的 LON/ETH 池
  * Sushiswap 上的 LON/USDT 池

目的
* 由社区投票决定激励力度，开启第二期流动性激励

提案执行项
* 根据提案投票结果实施激励，生效时间为 2021.1.21 4:00 UTC

投票选项
* A. 两个池分别获得 500,000 LON 作为二期流动性激励
* B. 两个池分别获得 600,000 LON 作为二期流动性激励
* C. 两个池分别获得 700,000 LON 作为二期流动性激励
* D. 两个池分别获得 800,000 LON 作为二期流动性激励
